summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 318, entitled "To provide for contracts for street improvements", approved October 13, 1882, and Ordinance No. 627, entitled "An Ordinance to amend Section Three of Ordinance No. 318", approved December 26, 1884, and Ordinance No. 1320, entitled "An Ordinance to amend Sections One, Two and Four of Ordinance No. 318, entitled "Ordinance No. 318 to provide for contracts for street improvements", approved October 13, 1882", approved April 7, 1890.
